            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>eggs </strong>to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>(salt prevents the eggs from cracking!) and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, cook for exactly 8 min for perfect, mid-boiled eggs, then fill a bowl with <strong>very cold water </strong>and add the <strong>cooked</strong> <strong>eggs</strong> to the bowl</p><p>Set aside to cool</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1612274748280-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
