            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the rice has had 9-10 min, stir in the <strong>blanched peas</strong> and the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>wilted spinach</strong></p><p>Increase the heat to medium and cook, covered, for a further 2-3 min or until the rice is cooked and the vegetables are warmed through – this is your <strong>green bean, spinach & pea</strong> <strong>vedgeree</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1612274764939-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1612274764939-x400.jpg",
