            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>green bean, spinach & pea</strong> <strong>vedgeree </strong>with the <strong>quartered eggs</strong> on top and the <strong>lemon wedges </strong>to the side, discard the cardamom pod<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></p><p>Drizzle the <strong>lemony mango chutney </strong>all over</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
